OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for most with
OL,6,Fdrizzle over western hills. Outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain move into northwest Scotland
OL,8,Fand Northern Ireland later. Dry
OL,9,Felsewhere and increasingly sunny
OL,10,Facross England and Wales. Feeling warm
OL,11,Fin the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain gradually eases across
OL,14,FScotland and Northern Ireland this
OL,15,Fevening. Clear skies elsewhere with
OL,16,Fmist and fog patches in England and
OL,17,FWales and a rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
