OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry for most with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. However, skies will be
OL,7,Fcloudier across parts of Scotland and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, with the odd spot of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. Warm in the sunshine.
